<p>[1] Schötz, Susanne &amp; van de Weijer, Joost &amp; Eklund, Robert. (2019). Phonetic Methods in Cat Vocalisation Studies: A report from the Meowsic project. 10.5281/zenodo.3245999. </p>
<p>[2] Schötz, Susanne. (2019). Paralinguistic Information and Biological Codes in Intra-and Interspecific Vocal Communication: A pilot study of Humans and Domestic Cats. 10.5281/zenodo.3246003. </p>
<p>[3] Schötz, Susanne &amp; van de Weijer, Joost &amp; Eklund, Robert. (2019). Melody matters: An acoustic study of domestic cat meows in six contexts and four mental states. 10.7287/peerj.preprints.27926. </p>
<p>[4] Gussenhoven, C. (2016), Foundations of Intonational Meaning: Anatomical and Physiological Factors. Top Cogn Sci,8:425-434. </p>
